title: My Coach
description:
My Coach helps coaches centralize client data and track progress. The beta version offers easy registration, public coach pages, and program requests with PDF responses.
Future Features
Custom PDF Generation: Create and customize PDFs directly.
Secure Payments: Seamless transactions.
Nutritional Guidance: Healthy food tips and recipes.
My Coach aims to be an all-in-one solution for fitness professionals and enthusiasts.
